  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study for AKB-6548 in Subjects With Chronic Kidney Disease and Anemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2a Open-Label Pilot Study to Assess the Pharmacodynamic Response, Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of 28-Day Repeat Oral Doses of AKB-6548 in Subjects With Anemia Secondary to Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD), Stages 3 and/or 4</official_title>
