  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, efficacy, and pharmacokinetics of repeat
      doses of orally administered AKB-6548 in pre-dialysis subjects with anemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
